graph TB
    subgraph "Feast Component"
        Operator[Feast Operator<br/>Go Controller]
        Online[Online Feature Store<br/>Python Service]
        Offline[Offline Feature Store<br/>Python Service]
        Registry[Registry Server<br/>Python gRPC/REST Service]
        UI[UI Server<br/>Python Service - Optional]
        CronJob[CronJob<br/>Materialization Tasks]

        Operator -->|manages| Online
        Operator -->|manages| Offline
        Operator -->|manages| Registry
        Operator -->|manages| UI
        Operator -->|manages| CronJob

        Online -->|queries metadata| Registry
        Offline -->|queries metadata| Registry
        CronJob -->|materializes to| Online
        CronJob -->|reads from| Offline
    end

    User[Data Scientist] -->|creates| FeatureStoreCR[FeatureStore CR]
    FeatureStoreCR -->|watched by| Operator

    Operator -->|creates| Deployments[Deployments]
    Operator -->|creates| Services[Services]
    Operator -->|creates| Routes[OpenShift Routes]
    Operator -->|creates| ConfigMaps[ConfigMaps]
    Operator -->|creates| PVCs[PersistentVolumeClaims]

    MLApp[ML Application] -->|POST /get-online-features| Online
    TrainingJob[Training Job] -->|POST /get-historical-features| Offline

    subgraph "Storage Backends"
        Redis[(Redis<br/>Online Store)]
        PostgreSQL[(PostgreSQL<br/>Registry/Online)]
        S3[(S3/GCS<br/>Offline Store)]
        SQLite[(SQLite<br/>Default)]
    end

    Online -->|reads features| Redis
    Online -->|reads features| PostgreSQL
    Online -->|reads features| SQLite
    Offline -->|reads historical data| S3
    Offline -->|reads historical data| PostgreSQL
    Registry -->|persists metadata| PostgreSQL
    Registry -->|persists metadata| S3

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API]
        Prometheus[Prometheus]
        OIDC[OIDC Provider]
        CertManager[cert-manager]
    end

    Operator -->|manages resources| K8sAPI
    Operator -->|exposes metrics| Prometheus
    Online -->|authenticates| OIDC
    Offline -->|authenticates| OIDC
    Registry -->|authenticates| OIDC
    UI -->|authenticates| OIDC
    Operator -->|requests certs| CertManager

    subgraph "ODH Integration"
        Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
        TrustedCA[Trusted CA Bundle]
    end

    Dashboard -->|discovers| FeatureStoreCR
    Operator -->|injects| TrustedCA

    style Operator fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Online fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Offline fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Registry fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style UI fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style CronJob fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style FeatureStoreCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Redis fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style PostgreSQL fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style S3 fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style SQLite fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style K8sAPI fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style Prometheus fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style OIDC fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style CertManager fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style Dashboard fill:#d5e8d4,stroke:#82b366
    style TrustedCA fill:#d5e8d4,stroke:#82b366
